<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n34ffvb"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n34" href="#n34ffvb">N34 (VI.B.27)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n34all.htm#n34ffvb">front flyleaf verso(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font color="green">[of]</font> 1<sup>st</sup> 7 Councils</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><font color="green">[The OEC]</font> consists of&nbsp;(a) those churches which have accepted all the decrees of the <mark>first seven general councils</mark>, and have remained in full communion with one another, and&nbsp;(b) such churches as have derived their origin from these by missionary activity, or by abscission <font color="green">[cutting off]</font> without loss of communion. <small> &ldquo;ORTHODOX EASTERN CHURCH&rdquo; <a name="EBOEC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#EBOEC"><cite title="source">Encyclopaedia Britannica</cite></a>, 11th edit. (1911) 333</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
